OSPF - Features


Most used IGP
IPv4 only -- OSPFv3 implements IPv6
Link State Protocol
Implemented as own IP protocol (not TCP or UDP)
Router discovery via multicast
Support for areas to divide network
IETF designed
super complex and badly documented protocol


